{"tid":1590742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［激多圖］大波警犬就識follow 呢班靚女冇人理？","createTime":"2019-09-24T01:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:32:09.000Z","uid":220479,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d23452231571165a24de135a24d1b4f9545f2078","tid":1590742,"uid":220479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係維吾爾族靚女啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhYdeV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhYdeV5.jpg&h=678c849a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AaDpmA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAaDpmA6.jpg&h=3978bd86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYo8Of6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYo8Of6.jpg&h=d3419a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你成班連登仔<br />\nJ圖就識睇<br />\n行動post就唔撚識推<br />\n知唔知929咩事呀？<br />\n全球反共反極權遊行呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.29公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3765f845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7RKmEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7RKmEb.jpg&h=76a53e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-新疆集中營<br />\n<br />\n呢班維吾爾族嘅靚女好可能日日就喺集中營入面被班支那蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你地班連登仔可唔可以響應精蟲嘅號召，一齊出嚟保護呢班維吾爾族靚女？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個核彈：新疆校長即將被處決<br />\n詳情唔多講，想知就睇返我上個post：<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">［核彈］新疆校長即將被處決 聲援新疆係新戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />